  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: "IGM: Hey so my friend has been petrified but I
    kinda wanna apply something to make her like that for a while without being scared?\n\nIGM:
    She says she enjoys the experience a lot. When she's not a statue. \n\nIGM: She
    just needs some like... mix of a berry and a petrification potion.\n\n"
